<HEADLINE> Tibet Elects Deputies To National People's Congress </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LHASA, January 15 (Xinhua) -- At the Sixth Session of the Sixth
People's Congress of the Tibet Autonomous Region today, 20
deputies to the Ninth National People's Congress were elected
through a secret ballot process.
</P>
<P>
Eighty-two percent of the new deputies are from ethnic minority
groups. 
</P>
