case filed by High Appeals Court Chief Prosecutor Vural Savas for
closure of the RP.
</P>
<P>
Savas opened the case at the Constitutional Court on May 21,
1997 demanding the Islamist party be shut down on the grounds of
its support for fundamentalism. 
