<HEADLINE> China Begins Production of Digital Video Discs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DALIAN, January 16 (Xinhua) -- China started production of
digital video discs (DVD) in Dalian city in northeast China's
Liaoning Province on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The China Hualu Matsushita Video Co. Ltd., a Sino-Japanese
joint venture in Dalian, expects to turn out 500 DVDs this
month. The output will be doubled since February.
</P>
<P>
