<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, January 16 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Secretary of Defense
William Cohen is expected to pay an official visit to Turkey in
the second week of February, the semi-official Anatolia News
Agency reported Friday.
</P>
<P>
