<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, January 16 (Xinhua) -- Indonesian badminton star Mia
Audina failed in her defense of the women's singles title when she
crashed to Chinese number seven Wang Chen in the quarter-finals at
the Japan Open here on Friday.
</P>
