<HEADLINE> Book on Marriage Life Published </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, January 16 (Xinhua) -- A book entitled "Red Book on
Marriage", which introduces knowledge on marriage life, has been
published by the Xinhua Publishing House.
</P>
<P>
The book consists of 10 chapters including knowledge on
marriage preparation, marriage ethics, marriage life, reproduction
care, child breeding and family harmony.
</P>
<P>
A survey shows that 72.6 percent of Shanghai's young people
want to learn more on marriage life and reproduction care.
