<DATE_TIME> 1998-01-16 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Television Tube Producer Successful </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XI'AN, January 16 (Xinhua) -- A leading Chinese television tube
producer has successfully produced China's first 40-cm color
television tube recently.
</P>
<P>
The Caihong Color Vacuum Television Tube Factory has invested
over 600 million yuan (72.289 million US dollars) in setting up a
production center capable of turning out one million 40-cm color
television tubes a year.
</P>
<P>
Located in Xianyang City, Shaanxi Province, Caihong is China's
first color television tube producer which began operation in
1982, employing complete set of equipment imported from Japan.
</P>
<P>
The factory is now capable of producing eight million tubes a
year, with annual output value reaching five billion yuan. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
